{"tid":898885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錯過下車地點　長沙老婦以跳窗迫停巴士","createTime":"2018-11-12T04:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T04:53:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77c2eba04bc16cc59bcfc545a3caeca1e2801fe2","tid":898885,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181112/s00004/3bab88a0f6d4b8c73b6ebc479353208b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181112%2Fs00004%2F3bab88a0f6d4b8c73b6ebc479353208b.jpg&h=eece95cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181112/s00004/3bddc22e0de743e3e657869478fc98b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181112%2Fs00004%2F3bddc22e0de743e3e657869478fc98b7.jpg&h=472b6f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重慶近日一宗乘客搶司機軚盤致巴士墜江事件，引起內地輿論關注乘客操守問題。在湖南長沙，昨（10日）再度傳出類似事件。一名老婦因錯過下車地點，要求司機停車不果後，竟然試圖以跳窗迫停巴士，幸而車上兩名乘客及時抱住老婦，才未釀成慘劇。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生在昨晨9時40分，當時巴士駛至一個路口時，這名老婦突然要求司機開門下車。司機多番拒絕後，這名老婦突然探出車窗試圖跳車。車上兩名女乘客大驚，隨即上前抱住老婦，而司機亦在附近一個安全位置停車，讓老婦下車了事。<br />\n<br />\n司機指當時非常緊張，表示從事30多年司機工作以來，從未遇過相關情況，呼籲乘客日後出現類似情況時應控制情緒，在下一個站下車後再轉乘另一架巴士返程，以策安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181112/s00004/1541993757026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181112%2Fs00004%2F1541993757026&d=zph2WZKeb6R4q%2F4bFgbe7AHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=cbcfd855\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181112%2Fs00004%2F1541993757026&h=6e076ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181112/s00004/1541993757026</a>"},{"pid":"ea07ef6d49428b3efab3c1c1c65cd93d0719279c","tid":898885,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:06